<item>
            <title>[LU-16818] replay-single test_65a: @@@@@@ FAIL: No early reply </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16818</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;replay-single/65a can fail on a local setup: with @@@@@@ FAIL: No early reply&lt;br/&gt;
this happens because OBD_FAIL_PTLRPC_PAUSE_REQ pauses any RPC except OBD_PING, but if MDS share the node with OST, then another RPC like OST_PRECREATE can hit the pause (which is supposed to happen just once).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
